descriptionHtml:
# Beat the moment you want to remember for a long time!
Take a trip with your sweetheart, a delicious meal with your parents, and the moment your child first walks around!
You can check the memories of the day with AR at the place even after time passes.

# Whenever I want to know, I want to share the moment with 'doodle'.
You can leave them with a wide range of openings. My comfortable room is private, my mom and dog happy hours can be seen only by my family, and my restaurant list should be open to the public. You can share more information and daily life with your followers.

# Enjoy AR with a sense of presence!
Now, when you run 'doodle', you can see AR, as well as articles, photos, videos, and popular tags left by others. What if nothing? Become the first 'doodler' here!

#Feel free to paint this place now!
Augmented reality (AR) allows you to draw your desired picture with a variety of brushes.
Drawings can be left in that location using GPS, and pictures left behind by others can be viewed in that location. Share your picture with others through space, not simply with AR.
